[SN]TITLE[SN]
Nicky Deverdics: Dover Athletic re-sign Hartlepool United midfielder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Dover Athletic have re-signed Hartlepool United midfielder Nicky Deverdics on a one-month loan deal.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 29-year-old has scored two goals in 24 appearances since joining Pools from the Whites last summer.
Deverdics spent two years with Dover after moving to Crabble in the summer of 2014, and scored 16 goals in all competitions last season.
He is eligible to play for Chris Kinnear's side against Wrexham in the National League on Saturday.
